arts.ttl: France vs Ukraine – The likely starting lineup for Les Bleus with Barcola and Cherki
arts.sum: This Thursday, the French national team will play Ukraine in a 2026 World Cup qualifier at 8:45 PM at the Parc des Princes. Five Paris Saint-Germain players will be involved in the match: four for France (Lucas Chevalier, Lucas Hernandez, Warren Zaïre-Emery, and Bradley Barcola) and one for Ukraine (Ilya Zabarnyi).
